00197         void OMax_date2state_do(t_OMax_date2state *x, long date)
00198         {
00199                 if (OMax_date2state_bind(x)&&(x->dataname->s_thing))
00200                 {
00201                         ATOMIC_INCREMENT(&(((t_OMax_data *)(x->dataname->s_thing))->readcount));
00202                         if(!(((t_OMax_data *)(x->dataname->s_thing))->wflag))
00203                         {
00204                                 if (x->data->get_size()>0 && date>=0)
00205                                 {
00206                                         switch(x->datatype)

00208                                                 case LETTERS:
00209                                                         outlet_int(x->out, date+1); // output
00210                                                         break;
00211                                                 default:
00212                                                         outlet_int(x->out, x->data->get_state(date)); // output
00213                                                         break;
00214                                         }
00215                                 }
00216                         }
00217                         else
00218                                 object_error((t_object *)x,"Data of Oracle %s busy",x->oname->s_name);
00219                         ATOMIC_DECREMENT(&(((t_OMax_data *)(x->dataname->s_thing))->readcount));
